messages.text: Vera.
I know you’re there…
Hi Casey.
Ready for your big date? ;)
If you mean ready to bring this creep down, then yes.
How far are you going to let it go?
According to the file he’s going to wine and dine me, sleep with me, then dump me.
So, you’re going all the way?
NO. I’m not sleeping with him.
I’m going to make him think he’s got a chance...
and then on our fourth date, you post the article.
So you’re setting the editorial schedule now?
I want to see the look on his face.
But for tonight it’s just playing along right?
For tonight it’s all wine and roses.
Well, good luck. Keep me in the loop.
I will :)
Tonight’s the night!
It is indeed.
You taking her to the place I recommended?
Table for two at 8pm @ Elsinore.
What is vegan Nordic food?
Wild edibles. Vera’s really into them.
Fantastic…
Are you sure you’re ready?
Bird in hand my friend. This is where I shine.
All right. Keep me up to date.
I’ll text you when it’s all over.
It’s just a date, right?
Relax, Graham. All tonight ends with is a harmless kiss.
R u there yet?
YES.
What are you wearing?
A red cocktail dress. Why?
No reason.
Are you here?
No.
Yes, you are! I see you!!!
That’s not me.
It is you! How did you even get a reservation?
HEY. I have connections.
I can’t believe you’re staking me out!
Relax. I’m just here if you need me!
Just don’t do anything weird.
Can’t be any weirder than this food. What is kelp spread?
He’s here!
How’s it going?
Just stepping inside. All good.
All good? Aren't you late?
Don’t want to appear too eager, Graham.
Are you on crutches?
Yes. High ankle sprain, remember?
How do you even know that?
Graham. Are you here???
Maybe.
I just want to watch.
Where are you? Are you that redheaded dude???
This is seriously cramping my style.
I won’t do anything. Scouts honor :)
You really did a number on him.
Shh.
He’s actually kind of hot!
Aw. You pulled his chair out for him.
Chivalry isn’t dead.
He’s kind of pathetic with that cast on.
Wounded animals are the most dangerous.
What’s he ordering?
Axelberries with wood sorrel.
WHAT?
I don’t even know why we’re here. This was Graham’s favorite restaurant.
Did you get the axelberries? So good.
U sure she likes this place? She made a face.
She loves it. We used to go here all the time.
If you’re feeling adventurous, try the pine needle medley.
I’ll keep it in mind…
Is there anything edible on this menu?
God, I hate this place.
What’s he talking about?
Music. He keeps talking about the Shins.
They were like my favorite band five years ago.
Looks like Graham gave him bad intel.
Right now I’d say his game is batting zero.
Graham… Did you give me bad intel?
What? No. What do you mean?
She just gagged on her wood sorrel.
Why? The wood sorrel here is fantastic!
Okay, switching to plan B.
What r u doing???
Where are you going?
He said the food here was terrible.
He’s improvising.
We’re going to shake shack!
I LOVE SHAKE SHACK!
ME TOO!
What are you doing? She HATES shake shack!
Are you following me?
It’s not that hard when you’re on crutches.
You gotta back off man. Let me do my thing.
How do you know she’ll like shake shack?
Idk! Because I like it!
I’m at the Shake Shack in the park. Where r u guys?
We’re over by the jazz band. The saxophonist is killing it.
He just gave them some cash.
OMG. They’re playing Paper Moon! I used to sing this in college.
What r u doing???
Sometimes you gotta switch things up. Call an audible.
Paper moon?
It’s my favorite jazz standard. I never pass up a chance to hear it.
This is supposed to be about Vera!
Hate to break it to you. I think she likes it.
I think I see you. Are you DANCING???
You look ridiculous!
You guys made quite a scene.
It just sort of happened.
He’s a really good dancer for a guy in a cast.
If you ask me, it looked like you might be enjoying yourself.
Don’t worry. I know it’s just a game.
Was dancing part of the plan?
Graham. Sometimes my job is actually fun.
Until you break their hearts.
Don’t worry. I always seal the deal. Now it’s time to plant that kiss.
OMG! He’s leaning in!
VERA!?
I can’t believe I have to watch this.
VERA?
Hey.
YOU KISSED HIM.
No. He kissed me.
It looked sort of simultaneous.
Have to play along, right?
How was it?
It was…
Good.
One date down.
Yeah. One date down.
You’re not getting cold feet are you?
No. Never. He has no idea what he’s in for.
That kiss was a little more than harmless…
Graham. Do me a favor. Don’t follow me again.
Why? I’m paying you.
Not to have you spy. If you do it again, I’ll tell her.
WHAT? Then I’ll sue you.
Sure. Good luck with that. Just lay off, all right?
Fine. But you better produce results.
Don’t worry, I’m always on my game.
Hey.
Hey…
I had a great time tonight.
Me too.
I don’t usually say this but you’re different.
Really? That’s not a line you use on all the girls ;)
No. I mean it. I really had fun.
Me too…
